# 🎂 Age Calculator Web App

A responsive and interactive **Age Calculator** built using **HTML**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **JavaScript**. Users can enter their date of birth, and the app calculates and displays their age in **years, months, and days**, complete with animated counting and dark mode support.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📅 **Input Validation** for day, month, and year.
- 🧮 Calculates precise **age** in:
  - Years
  - Months
  - Days
- 🎞️ Smooth **number animation** when showing age.
- 🌗 Toggleable **dark mode** (with localStorage persistence).
- ⚠️ User-friendly **error messages** for invalid input.
- 💡 Responsive design using **Tailwind CSS**.
- ✨ Scroll-based animations with **AOS (Animate On Scroll)**.

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- **HTML5**
- **Tailwind CSS**
- **JavaScript (ES6)**
- [AOS.js](https://michalsnik.github.io/aos/)
- [Font Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/)

